snippet.title: Bomb Rush Cyberfunk - Official Special Trailer
snippet.description:
Bomb Rush Cyberfunk is coming out on Steam & Nintendo Switch at 18 Augustus 2023 and Playstation & Xbox at 1 September 2023

Price: $39,99* 

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1353230/Bomb_Rush_Cyberfunk/
Wishlist on the Nintendo eShop: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/bomb-rush-cyberfunk-switch/

Footage from this trailer has been captured on a Nintendo Switch 

Music: GRRL - OPERATOR
Thumbnail Graffiti: 3DROD - OVERWHELMME

*Regional currencies might result in a different price point
